name: Fay - GameJam vom 09.11.2019
description:
This is the resulting prototype of a story based game, we created for the 24h GameJam in Bern.

Find the right objects to interact with and experience a lovely story (or at least some parts of it).

Team: Eugénie, Markus and Michael
